articles.title: Google says its updated Gemini 2.5 Pro AI model is better at coding - TechCrunch
articles.description: Google says the update to its Gemini 2.5 Pro preview model is better at certain programming tasks and builds on the upgrade to Gemini 2.5 Pro the company announced around a month ago.
articles.content:
Google on Thursday announced an update to its Gemini 2.5 Pro preview model that the company claims is better at certain programming tasks.
